{
  "video_id": "IjbTiRbeNpM",
  "title": "How AI can bring on a second Industrial Revolution | Kevin Kelly",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 14966.0,
      "end_time": 19509.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m going to talk a little bit about where technology&#39;s going."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 19509.0,
      "end_time": 22566.0,
      "text": "And often technology comes to us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 22566.0,
      "end_time": 24455.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re surprised by what it brings."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 24455.0,
      "end_time": 28162.0,
      "text": "But there&#39;s actually a large aspect of technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 28162.0,
      "end_time": 29988.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s much more predictable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 29988.0,
      "end_time": 34100.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s because technological systems of all sorts have leanings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 34100.0,
      "end_time": 35299.0,
      "text": "they have urgencies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 35299.0,
      "end_time": 36884.0,
      "text": "they have tendencies."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 36884.0,
      "end_time": 41840.0,
      "text": "And those tendencies are derived from the very nature of the physics,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 41840.0,
      "end_time": 45659.0,
      "text": "chemistry of wires and switches and electrons,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 45659.0,
      "end_time": 49745.0,
      "text": "and they will make reoccurring patterns again and again."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 49745.0,
      "end_time": 54643.0,
      "text": "And so those patterns produce these tendencies, these leanings."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 54643.0,
      "end_time": 57498.0,
      "text": "You can almost think of it as sort of like gravity."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 57498.0,
      "end_time": 59841.0,
      "text": "Imagine raindrops falling into a valley."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 59841.0,
      "end_time": 62953.0,
      "text": "The actual path of a raindrop as it goes down the valley"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 62953.0,
      "end_time": 64651.0,
      "text": "is unpredictable."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 64650.99999999999,
      "end_time": 66193.0,
      "text": "We cannot see where it&#39;s going,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 66193.0,
      "end_time": 68494.0,
      "text": "but the general direction is very inevitable:"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 68494.0,
      "end_time": 70377.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s downward."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 70377.0,
      "end_time": 74973.0,
      "text": "And so these baked-in tendencies and urgencies"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 74973.0,
      "end_time": 77051.0,
      "text": "in technological systems"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 77051.0,
      "end_time": 81149.0,
      "text": "give us a sense of where things are going at the large form."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 81149.0,
      "end_time": 82574.0,
      "text": "So in a large sense,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 82574.0,
      "end_time": 87005.0,
      "text": "I would say that telephones were inevitable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 87005.0,
      "end_time": 89094.0,
      "text": "but the iPhone was not."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 89094.0,
      "end_time": 91274.0,
      "text": "The Internet was inevitable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 91274.0,
      "end_time": 93036.0,
      "text": "but Twitter was not."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 93036.0,
      "end_time": 96988.0,
      "text": "So we have many ongoing tendencies right now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 96988.0,
      "end_time": 99732.0,
      "text": "and I think one of the chief among them"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 99732.0,
      "end_time": 104041.0,
      "text": "is this tendency to make things smarter and smarter."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 104041.0,
      "end_time": 106783.0,
      "text": "I call it cognifying -- cognification --"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 106783.0,
      "end_time": 110025.0,
      "text": "also known as artificial intelligence, or AI."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 110025.0,
      "end_time": 113795.0,
      "text": "And I think that&#39;s going to be one of the most influential developments"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 113795.0,
      "end_time": 120021.0,
      "text": "and trends and directions and drives in our society in the next 20 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 120021.0,
      "end_time": 122030.0,
      "text": "So, of course, it&#39;s already here."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 122030.0,
      "end_time": 124258.0,
      "text": "We already have AI,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 124258.0,
      "end_time": 126680.0,
      "text": "and often it works in the background,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 126680.0,
      "end_time": 128290.0,
      "text": "in the back offices of hospitals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 128289.99999999999,
      "end_time": 133000.0,
      "text": "where it&#39;s used to diagnose X-rays better than a human doctor."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 133000.0,
      "end_time": 134750.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s in legal offices,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 134750.0,
      "end_time": 137142.0,
      "text": "where it&#39;s used to go through legal evidence"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 137142.0,
      "end_time": 139506.0,
      "text": "better than a human paralawyer."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 139506.0,
      "end_time": 144165.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s used to fly the plane that you came here with."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 144165.0,
      "end_time": 146570.0,
      "text": "Human pilots only flew it seven to eight minutes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 146570.0,
      "end_time": 148547.0,
      "text": "the rest of the time the AI was driving."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 148547.0,
      "end_time": 150744.0,
      "text": "And of course, in Netflix and Amazon,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 150744.0,
      "end_time": 153298.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s in the background, making those recommendations."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 153298.0,
      "end_time": 154583.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s what we have today."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 154583.0,
      "end_time": 159408.0,
      "text": "And we have an example, of course, in a more front-facing aspect of it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 159408.0,
      "end_time": 166478.0,
      "text": "with the win of the AlphaGo, who beat the world&#39;s greatest Go champion."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 166478.0,
      "end_time": 170555.0,
      "text": "But it&#39;s more than that."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 170555.0,
      "end_time": 173221.0,
      "text": "If you play a video game, you&#39;re playing against an AI."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 173221.0,
      "end_time": 177783.0,
      "text": "But recently, Google taught their AI"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 177783.0,
      "end_time": 180686.0,
      "text": "to actually learn how to play video games."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 180686.0,
      "end_time": 183419.0,
      "text": "Again, teaching video games was already done,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 183419.0,
      "end_time": 187340.0,
      "text": "but learning how to play a video game is another step."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 187340.0,
      "end_time": 190571.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s artificial smartness."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 190571.0,
      "end_time": 195117.0,
      "text": "What we&#39;re doing is taking this artificial smartness"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 195117.0,
      "end_time": 198710.0,
      "text": "and we&#39;re making it smarter and smarter."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 198710.0,
      "end_time": 202629.0,
      "text": "There are three aspects to this general trend"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 202629.0,
      "end_time": 204342.0,
      "text": "that I think are underappreciated;"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 204342.0,
      "end_time": 206643.0,
      "text": "I think we would understand AI a lot better"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 206643.0,
      "end_time": 208968.0,
      "text": "if we understood these three things."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 208968.0,
      "end_time": 212275.0,
      "text": "I think these things also would help us embrace AI,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 212275.0,
      "end_time": 215887.0,
      "text": "because it&#39;s only by embracing it that we actually can steer it."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 215887.0,
      "end_time": 219467.0,
      "text": "We can actually steer the specifics by embracing the larger trend."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 219467.0,
      "end_time": 222470.0,
      "text": "So let me talk about those three different aspects."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 222470.0,
      "end_time": 226167.0,
      "text": "The first one is: our own intelligence has a very poor understanding"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 226167.0,
      "end_time": 228110.0,
      "text": "of what intelligence is."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 228110.0,
      "end_time": 231787.0,
      "text": "We tend to think of intelligence as a single dimension,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 231787.0,
      "end_time": 234561.0,
      "text": "that it&#39;s kind of like a note that gets louder and louder."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 234561.0,
      "end_time": 237192.0,
      "text": "It starts like with IQ measurement."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 237192.0,
      "end_time": 241308.0,
      "text": "It starts with maybe a simple low IQ in a rat or mouse,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 241308.0,
      "end_time": 243887.0,
      "text": "and maybe there&#39;s more in a chimpanzee,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 243887.0,
      "end_time": 246102.0,
      "text": "and then maybe there&#39;s more in a stupid person,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 246102.0,
      "end_time": 248222.0,
      "text": "and then maybe an average person like myself,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 248222.0,
      "end_time": 249536.0,
      "text": "and then maybe a genius."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 249536.0,
      "end_time": 254516.0,
      "text": "And this single IQ intelligence is getting greater and greater."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 254516.0,
      "end_time": 255691.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s completely wrong."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 255691.0,
      "end_time": 259673.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s not what intelligence is -- not what human intelligence is, anyway."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 259673.0,
      "end_time": 264203.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s much more like a symphony of different notes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 264203.0,
      "end_time": 267836.0,
      "text": "and each of these notes is played on a different instrument of cognition."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 267836.0,
      "end_time": 271561.0,
      "text": "There are many types of intelligences in our own minds."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 271561.0,
      "end_time": 274633.0,
      "text": "We have deductive reasoning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 274633.0,
      "end_time": 276878.0,
      "text": "we have emotional intelligence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 276878.0,
      "end_time": 278295.0,
      "text": "we have spatial intelligence;"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 278295.0,
      "end_time": 282340.0,
      "text": "we have maybe 100 different types that are all grouped together,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 282340.0,
      "end_time": 286269.0,
      "text": "and they vary in different strengths with different people."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 286269.0,
      "end_time": 290819.0,
      "text": "And of course, if we go to animals, they also have another basket --"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 290819.0,
      "end_time": 293384.0,
      "text": "another symphony of different kinds of intelligences,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 293384.0,
      "end_time": 296974.0,
      "text": "and sometimes those same instruments are the same that we have."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 296974.0,
      "end_time": 300559.0,
      "text": "They can think in the same way, but they may have a different arrangement,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 300559.0,
      "end_time": 303050.0,
      "text": "and maybe they&#39;re higher in some cases than humans,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 303050.0,
      "end_time": 305911.0,
      "text": "like long-term memory in a squirrel is actually phenomenal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 305911.0,
      "end_time": 308222.0,
      "text": "so it can remember where it buried its nuts."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 308222.0,
      "end_time": 310233.0,
      "text": "But in other cases they may be lower."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 310233.0,
      "end_time": 312987.0,
      "text": "When we go to make machines,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 312987.0,
      "end_time": 315207.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re going to engineer them in the same way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 315207.0,
      "end_time": 320241.0,
      "text": "where we&#39;ll make some of those types of smartness much greater than ours,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 320241.0,
      "end_time": 322836.0,
      "text": "and many of them won&#39;t be anywhere near ours,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 322836.0,
      "end_time": 324404.0,
      "text": "because they&#39;re not needed."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 324404.0,
      "end_time": 326631.0,
      "text": "So we&#39;re going to take these things,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 326631.0,
      "end_time": 328736.0,
      "text": "these artificial clusters,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 328736.0,
      "end_time": 334507.0,
      "text": "and we&#39;ll be adding more varieties of artificial cognition to our AIs."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 334507.0,
      "end_time": 338602.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re going to make them very, very specific."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 338602.0,
      "end_time": 345168.0,
      "text": "So your calculator is smarter than you are in arithmetic already;"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 345168.0,
      "end_time": 349337.0,
      "text": "your GPS is smarter than you are in spatial navigation;"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 349337.0,
      "end_time": 354339.0,
      "text": "Google, Bing, are smarter than you are in long-term memory."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 354339.0,
      "end_time": 358893.0,
      "text": "And we&#39;re going to take, again, these kinds of different types of thinking"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 358893.0,
      "end_time": 360850.0,
      "text": "and we&#39;ll put them into, like, a car."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 360850.0,
      "end_time": 363931.0,
      "text": "The reason why we want to put them in a car so the car drives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 363931.0,
      "end_time": 366257.0,
      "text": "is because it&#39;s not driving like a human."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 366257.0,
      "end_time": 367677.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not thinking like us."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 367677.0,
      "end_time": 369621.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s the whole feature of it."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 369621.0,
      "end_time": 371180.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not being distracted,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 371180.0,
      "end_time": 373958.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s not worrying about whether it left the stove on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 373958.0,
      "end_time": 376120.0,
      "text": "or whether it should have majored in finance."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 376120.0,
      "end_time": 377297.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s just driving."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 377297.0,
      "end_time": 378463.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 378463.0,
      "end_time": 380328.0,
      "text": "Just driving, OK?"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 380328.0,
      "end_time": 383289.0,
      "text": "And we actually might even come to advertise these"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 383289.0,
      "end_time": 384858.0,
      "text": "as &quot;consciousness-free.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 384858.0,
      "end_time": 386656.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re without consciousness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 386656.0,
      "end_time": 388784.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re not concerned about those things,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 388784.0,
      "end_time": 389964.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re not distracted."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 389964.0,
      "end_time": 392954.0,
      "text": "So in general, what we&#39;re trying to do"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 392954.0,
      "end_time": 397804.0,
      "text": "is make as many different types of thinking as we can."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 397804.0,
      "end_time": 399911.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re going to populate the space"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 399911.0,
      "end_time": 404094.0,
      "text": "of all the different possible types, or species, of thinking."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 404094.0,
      "end_time": 406186.0,
      "text": "And there actually may be some problems"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 406186.0,
      "end_time": 409010.0,
      "text": "that are so difficult in business and science"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 409010.0,
      "end_time": 413076.0,
      "text": "that our own type of human thinking may not be able to solve them alone."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 413076.0,
      "end_time": 415092.0,
      "text": "We may need a two-step program,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 415092.0,
      "end_time": 419692.0,
      "text": "which is to invent new kinds of thinking"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 419692.0,
      "end_time": 423450.0,
      "text": "that we can work alongside of to solve these really large problems,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 423450.0,
      "end_time": 428496.0,
      "text": "say, like dark energy or quantum gravity."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 428496.0,
      "end_time": 431166.0,
      "text": "What we&#39;re doing is making alien intelligences."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 431166.0,
      "end_time": 435259.0,
      "text": "You might even think of this as, sort of, artificial aliens"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 435259.0,
      "end_time": 436490.0,
      "text": "in some senses."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 436490.0,
      "end_time": 438814.0,
      "text": "And they&#39;re going to help us think different,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 438814.0,
      "end_time": 442470.0,
      "text": "because thinking different is the engine of creation"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 442470.0,
      "end_time": 445835.0,
      "text": "and wealth and new economy."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 445835.0,
      "end_time": 450782.0,
      "text": "The second aspect of this is that we are going to use AI"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 450782.0,
      "end_time": 454135.0,
      "text": "to basically make a second Industrial Revolution."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 454135.0,
      "end_time": 456932.0,
      "text": "The first Industrial Revolution was based on the fact"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 456932.0,
      "end_time": 460879.0,
      "text": "that we invented something I would call artificial power."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 460879.0,
      "end_time": 462053.0,
      "text": "Previous to that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 462053.0,
      "end_time": 464111.0,
      "text": "during the Agricultural Revolution,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 464111.0,
      "end_time": 467837.0,
      "text": "everything that was made had to be made with human muscle"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 467837.0,
      "end_time": 469565.0,
      "text": "or animal power."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 469565.0,
      "end_time": 471652.0,
      "text": "That was the only way to get anything done."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 471652.0,
      "end_time": 474621.0,
      "text": "The great innovation during the Industrial Revolution was,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 474621.0,
      "end_time": 477754.0,
      "text": "we harnessed steam power, fossil fuels,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 477754.0,
      "end_time": 481634.0,
      "text": "to make this artificial power that we could use"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 481634.0,
      "end_time": 483327.0,
      "text": "to do anything we wanted to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 483327.0,
      "end_time": 486571.0,
      "text": "So today when you drive down the highway,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 486571.0,
      "end_time": 491120.0,
      "text": "you are, with a flick of the switch, commanding 250 horses --"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 491120.0,
      "end_time": 492716.0,
      "text": "250 horsepower --"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 492716.0,
      "end_time": 497432.0,
      "text": "which we can use to build skyscrapers, to build cities, to build roads,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 497432.0,
      "end_time": 503245.0,
      "text": "to make factories that would churn out lines of chairs or refrigerators"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 503245.0,
      "end_time": 504923.0,
      "text": "way beyond our own power."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 504923.0,
      "end_time": 511058.0,
      "text": "And that artificial power can also be distributed on wires on a grid"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 511058.0,
      "end_time": 514281.0,
      "text": "to every home, factory, farmstead,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 514280.99999999994,
      "end_time": 518495.99999999994,
      "text": "and anybody could buy that artificial power,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 518496.0,
      "end_time": 519992.0,
      "text": "just by plugging something in."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 519991.99999999994,
      "end_time": 522454.99999999994,
      "text": "So this was a source of innovation as well,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 522455.00000000006,
      "end_time": 525897.0,
      "text": "because a farmer could take a manual hand pump,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 525897.0,
      "end_time": 528837.0,
      "text": "and they could add this artificial power, this electricity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 528837.0,
      "end_time": 530358.0,
      "text": "and he&#39;d have an electric pump."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 530358.0,
      "end_time": 533700.0,
      "text": "And you multiply that by thousands or tens of thousands of times,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 533700.0,
      "end_time": 536883.0,
      "text": "and that formula was what brought us the Industrial Revolution."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 536883.0,
      "end_time": 540492.0,
      "text": "All the things that we see, all this progress that we now enjoy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 540492.0,
      "end_time": 542579.0,
      "text": "has come from the fact that we&#39;ve done that."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 542579.0,
      "end_time": 544951.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re going to do the same thing now with AI."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 544951.0,
      "end_time": 547050.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re going to distribute that on a grid,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 547050.0,
      "end_time": 549448.0,
      "text": "and now you can take that electric pump."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 549448.0,
      "end_time": 552440.0,
      "text": "You can add some artificial intelligence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 552440.0,
      "end_time": 553945.0,
      "text": "and now you have a smart pump."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 553945.0,
      "end_time": 555897.0,
      "text": "And that, multiplied by a million times,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 555897.0,
      "end_time": 558284.0,
      "text": "is going to be this second Industrial Revolution."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 558284.0,
      "end_time": 560690.0,
      "text": "So now the car is going down the highway,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 560690.0,
      "end_time": 565008.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s 250 horsepower, but in addition, it&#39;s 250 minds."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 565008.0,
      "end_time": 566801.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s the auto-driven car."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 566801.0,
      "end_time": 568214.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s like a new commodity;"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 568214.0,
      "end_time": 569541.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s a new utility."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 569541.0,
      "end_time": 572606.0,
      "text": "The AI is going to flow across the grid -- the cloud --"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 572606.0,
      "end_time": 574197.0,
      "text": "in the same way electricity did."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 574197.0,
      "end_time": 576601.0,
      "text": "So everything that we had electrified,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 576601.0,
      "end_time": 578693.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re now going to cognify."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 578693.0,
      "end_time": 580102.0,
      "text": "And I would suggest, then,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 580102.0,
      "end_time": 583858.0,
      "text": "that the formula for the next 10,000 start-ups"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 583858.0,
      "end_time": 585044.0,
      "text": "is very, very simple,"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 585044.0,
      "end_time": 589100.0,
      "text": "which is to take x and add AI."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 589100.0,
      "end_time": 591936.0,
      "text": "That is the formula, that&#39;s what we&#39;re going to be doing."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 591936.0,
      "end_time": 595266.0,
      "text": "And that is the way in which we&#39;re going to make"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 595266.0,
      "end_time": 597148.0,
      "text": "this second Industrial Revolution."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 597148.0,
      "end_time": 599326.0,
      "text": "And by the way -- right now, this minute,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 599326.0,
      "end_time": 600519.0,
      "text": "you can log on to Google"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 600519.0,
      "end_time": 604758.0,
      "text": "and you can purchase AI for six cents, 100 hits."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 604758.0,
      "end_time": 606386.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s available right now."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 606386.0,
      "end_time": 609315.0,
      "text": "So the third aspect of this"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 609315.0,
      "end_time": 612017.0,
      "text": "is that when we take this AI and embody it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 612017.0,
      "end_time": 613214.0,
      "text": "we get robots."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 613214.0,
      "end_time": 614941.0,
      "text": "And robots are going to be bots,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 614941.0,
      "end_time": 620357.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re going to be doing many of the tasks that we have already done."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 620357.0,
      "end_time": 621909.0,
      "text": "A job is just a bunch of tasks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 621909.0,
      "end_time": 623695.0,
      "text": "so they&#39;re going to redefine our jobs"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 623695.0,
      "end_time": 625978.0,
      "text": "because they&#39;re going to do some of those tasks."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 625978.0,
      "end_time": 629199.0,
      "text": "But they&#39;re also going to create whole new categories,"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 629199.0,
      "end_time": 631470.0,
      "text": "a whole new slew of tasks"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 631470.0,
      "end_time": 633951.0,
      "text": "that we didn&#39;t know we wanted to do before."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 633951.0,
      "end_time": 637612.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re going to actually engender new kinds of jobs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 637612.0,
      "end_time": 639907.0,
      "text": "new kinds of tasks that we want done,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 639907.0,
      "end_time": 643336.0,
      "text": "just as automation made up a whole bunch of new things"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 643336.0,
      "end_time": 645194.0,
      "text": "that we didn&#39;t know we needed before,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 645194.0,
      "end_time": 647174.0,
      "text": "and now we can&#39;t live without them."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 647174.0,
      "end_time": 651154.0,
      "text": "So they&#39;re going to produce even more jobs than they take away,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 651154.0,
      "end_time": 654612.0,
      "text": "but it&#39;s important that a lot of the tasks that we&#39;re going to give them"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 654612.0,
      "end_time": 659676.0,
      "text": "are tasks that can be defined in terms of efficiency or productivity."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 659676.0,
      "end_time": 661528.0,
      "text": "If you can specify a task,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 661528.0,
      "end_time": 663787.0,
      "text": "either manual or conceptual,"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 663787.0,
      "end_time": 668591.0,
      "text": "that can be specified in terms of efficiency or productivity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 668591.0,
      "end_time": 670758.0,
      "text": "that goes to the bots."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 670758.0,
      "end_time": 672960.0,
      "text": "Productivity is for robots."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 672960.0,
      "end_time": 676054.0,
      "text": "What we&#39;re really good at is basically wasting time."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 676054.0,
      "end_time": 677106.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 677106.0,
      "end_time": 679446.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re really good at things that are inefficient."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 679446.0,
      "end_time": 682816.0,
      "text": "Science is inherently inefficient."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 682816.0,
      "end_time": 685746.0,
      "text": "It runs on that fact that you have one failure after another."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 685746.0,
      "end_time": 689194.0,
      "text": "It runs on the fact that you make tests and experiments that don&#39;t work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 689194.0,
      "end_time": 690660.0,
      "text": "otherwise you&#39;re not learning."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 690660.0,
      "end_time": 691846.0,
      "text": "It runs on the fact"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 691846.0,
      "end_time": 693953.0,
      "text": "that there is not a lot of efficiency in it."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 693953.0,
      "end_time": 696756.0,
      "text": "Innovation by definition is inefficient,"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 696756.0,
      "end_time": 698171.0,
      "text": "because you make prototypes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 698171.0,
      "end_time": 700902.0,
      "text": "because you try stuff that fails, that doesn&#39;t work."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 700902.0,
      "end_time": 704038.0,
      "text": "Exploration is inherently inefficiency."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 704038.0,
      "end_time": 705593.0,
      "text": "Art is not efficient."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 705593.0,
      "end_time": 707744.0,
      "text": "Human relationships are not efficient."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 707744.0,
      "end_time": 710708.0,
      "text": "These are all the kinds of things we&#39;re going to gravitate to,"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 710708.0,
      "end_time": 712207.0,
      "text": "because they&#39;re not efficient."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 712207.0,
      "end_time": 715338.0,
      "text": "Efficiency is for robots."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 715338.0,
      "end_time": 719485.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re also going to learn that we&#39;re going to work with these AIs"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 719485.0,
      "end_time": 722005.0,
      "text": "because they think differently than us."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 722005.0,
      "end_time": 726343.0,
      "text": "When Deep Blue beat the world&#39;s best chess champion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 726343.0,
      "end_time": 728296.0,
      "text": "people thought it was the end of chess."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 728296.0,
      "end_time": 732722.0,
      "text": "But actually, it turns out that today, the best chess champion in the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 732722.0,
      "end_time": 734906.0,
      "text": "is not an AI."
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 734906.0,
      "end_time": 736111.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s not a human."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 736111.0,
      "end_time": 738850.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s the team of a human and an AI."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 738850.0,
      "end_time": 742874.0,
      "text": "The best medical diagnostician is not a doctor, it&#39;s not an AI,"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 742874.0,
      "end_time": 744074.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s the team."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 744074.0,
      "end_time": 746247.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re going to be working with these AIs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 746247.0,
      "end_time": 748266.0,
      "text": "and I think you&#39;ll be paid in the future"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 748266.0,
      "end_time": 751026.0,
      "text": "by how well you work with these bots."
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 751026.0,
      "end_time": 755307.0,
      "text": "So that&#39;s the third thing, is that they&#39;re different,"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 755307.0,
      "end_time": 756496.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re utility"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 756496.0,
      "end_time": 760336.0,
      "text": "and they are going to be something we work with rather than against."
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 760336.0,
      "end_time": 762999.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re working with these rather than against them."
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 762999.0,
      "end_time": 764500.0,
      "text": "So, the future:"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 764500.0,
      "end_time": 765944.0,
      "text": "Where does that take us?"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 765944.0,
      "end_time": 769535.0,
      "text": "I think that 25 years from now, they&#39;ll look back"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 769535.0,
      "end_time": 772684.0,
      "text": "and look at our understanding of AI and say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 772684.0,
      "end_time": 776008.0,
      "text": "&quot;You didn&#39;t have AI. In fact, you didn&#39;t even have the Internet yet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 776008.0,
      "end_time": 779849.0,
      "text": "compared to what we&#39;re going to have 25 years from now.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 779849.0,
      "end_time": 782920.0,
      "text": "There are no AI experts right now."
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 782920.0,
